---
import { shared } from "../data/landing";
---

<section class="bg-page py-20 sm:py-24" aria-labelledby="premium-brief-title">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[0.82fr_1.18fr]">
      <div class="rounded-[2.25rem] border border-border bg-panel p-8 shadow-soft lg:p-10">
        <p class="text-sm font-extrabold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-primary">Leitura técnica</p>
        <h2 id="premium-brief-title" class="mt-4 text-balance font-display text-3xl font-black tracking-[-0.04em] text-ink sm:text-5xl">
          Antes de vender limpeza, mostramos o que será protegido.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-medium leading-8 text-muted">
          A versão premium posiciona a Split Limpo como serviço técnico: menos pressa visual, mais método, mais controle e mais segurança na decisão.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-[2.25rem] border border-primary/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-panel via-panel to-primary/10 p-6 shadow-soft lg:p-8">
        <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
          {shared.process.map((step, index) => (
            <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-border bg-page/58 p-5">
              <span class="font-display text-4xl font-black text-primary/70">0{index + 1}</span>
              <h3 class="mt-8 font-display text-xl font-black tracking-tight text-ink">{step.title}</h3>
              <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-muted">{step.description}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 rounded-[1.75rem] border border-border bg-page/60 p-5 md:grid-cols-3">
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-black text-accent">1h-1h30</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-xs font-extrabold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-muted">tempo médio</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-black text-accent">0</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-xs font-extrabold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-muted">remoção da parede</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-black text-accent">3</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-xs font-extrabold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-muted">etapas visíveis</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
